FILM INFORMATION :

Jacob is a young man used to getting everything he wants. For several years,
he has been living in a happy homosexual partnership with J&oslash;rgen,and one night Jacob decides
to pop the big question to J&oslash;rgen. J&oslash;rgen happily accepts Jacobs marriage proposal, 
but then something happens: Jacob falls in love with a girl,and not just any girl.
The girl is Caroline, married to J&oslash;rgens younger brother Tom. Jacobs life suddenly gets very complicated,
trying to figure out whether he wants to spend his lifewith J&oslash;rgen or Caroline. Most of all, 
he wants both! When Caroline gets pregnant with Jacob, matters are even more complicated. The story features 
many hilarious and akward situations between Jacob,J&oslash;rgen, Caroline and their many gay and straight friends.
